* `mod + b` switches to horizontal layout

* `sway move workspace to output (right|left|down|up)`

* `sway output <output> pos 0 0` to move <output> to left of primary screen

* `sway output <output> scale 2` for 4k screens

* `sway output <output> mode 1920x1080` to set the screen resolution for <output> to 1080p
